     Complete nicknames and commands (programmable)

`fill'
     Wrap long lines

`identd'
     Launch an identd server on port 8113

`irccontrols'
     Highlight or remove IRC control characters

`log'
     Save buffers in logs

`match'
     Highlight pals, fools, and other keywords

